<p><a name="Examples" id="Examples"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Lissajous_curve&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1" title="Edit section: Examples">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Examples</span></h2>
<p>Below are examples of Lissajous figures with <i>δ</i> = <i>π</i>/2, an odd <a href="/wiki/Natural_number" title="Natural number">natural number</a> <i>a</i>, an even <a href="/wiki/Natural_number" title="Natural number">natural number</a> <i>b</i>, and |<i>a</i>&#160;−&#160;<i>b</i>|&#160;=&#160;1.</p>
